&lt;p&gt;The Channel Manager will build, enable, and scale Unframe’s partner ecosystem. This role is responsible for developing strategic partnerships (VARs, GSIs, MSPs and technology partners), driving sourced and influenced revenue, and ensuring partners are effectively enabled to position and sell Unframe solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work cross-functionally with Sales, Marketing, Product, and Customer Success to create a repeatable, scalable partner motion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
