&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an Engineering Tech Lead to help drive some of the most strategic technical initiatives at Unframe.&amp;nbsp;This is not a traditional Tech Lead role.&amp;nbsp;We’re looking for someone who is deeply technical and highly hands-on, but also knows how to think strategically, lead architecture decisions, and represent the company in front of enterprise customers and senior stakeholders.&amp;nbsp;You’ll work across multiple teams and domains, partnering closely with Platform, Product, and Engineering teams to design and deliver AI-powered enterprise solutions at scale.&amp;nbsp;One moment you might be deep in architecture or code, and the next you’ll be in a room with customer executives helping guide critical technical decisions. We work on site from our offices in Tel Aviv.&lt;/p&gt;
