&lt;li&gt;Stay deeply hands-on with the code and engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive complex technical decisions across scalability, reliability, performance, and system design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help customers solve real production challenges and build long-term technical trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design versatile enterprise-grade solutions across different customer environments and use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence engineering standards, architecture practices, and long-term technical direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate in a fast-moving, high-ownership environment where execution speed matters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
