&lt;li&gt;Strong hands-on experience with Node.js, TypeScript, and modern frontend frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep experience designing scalable production systems and distributed architectures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong architectural thinking combined with a builder mentality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with enterprise customers or large-scale deployments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building AI/LLM-powered products or platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and ability to lead technical conversations with both engineers and executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High ownership mentality and ability to operate independently in ambiguous environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone equally comfortable writing code, designing systems, and speaking with customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
